Detailed Description

A structure containing ephemeris data elements supported by GPStream products.

Attention:
Both GPS and Glonass assistance will be delivered in this format.

Please refer to the ICD-GPS-200 Rev C or IS-GPS-200 Rev D for more information on the elements included within this structure. Assume a scale factor of 1.0 if not specified otherwise.

See also:
RXN_Set_Ephemeris()
RXN_Get_Ephemeris()
Since:
1.1.0
